channel.title: Please Help... Really Need It
channel.description:
[i]I was going through my server one day and i noticed that i could delete objects put there by moparscape. I tried it out and compiled re-ran server and the object was there so i stop the server and restarted it and it was there...[/i]
[b]What can i do to remove the part where when you have to turn off the server and restart it just to see that the object is no longer there?
And Yes When You Log In You Have The Code Inserted[/b]
[code] Deleteobjects(); Deletewalls(); [/code]
